description: This NFT entitles the owner to claim the Bitcoin Pizza #79831 (InscriptionID: 11b1e726ba46c77c70f8d56ea6b791bd7f3d3bda89416127fb2f4098041f5468i0) inscribed on the Bitcoin Blockchain.
